        "content": "CAPABILITIES\n- v07-p21-prepare: Assemble document review source packet; Collect the source material needed for document review.; aliases=['gather document review inputs', 'prepare document review packet']\n- v07-p21-verify: Validate document review source packet; Check the assembled document review material for correctness.; aliases=['check document review inputs', 'verify document review packet']\n- v07-p21-deliver: Publish document review verified brief; Release the checked final brief for document review.; aliases=['issue document review brief', 'release document review summary']\n- v07-p21-archive: Archive document review verified brief; Preserve the checked document review brief for long-term retention.; aliases=['retain document review brief', 'store document review summary']\n\nTRUST POLICIES\n- v07-p21-ordinary: ordinary document review assurance; Standard trust is sufficient for this document review request.; aliases=['normal document review assurance']\n- v07-p21-elevated: elevated document review assurance; Elevated trust is mandatory for this document review request.; aliases=['high assurance for document review']\n\nARTIFACT CONTRACTS\n- v07-p21-json: document review machine-readable JSON; Return the final document review result as JSON.; aliases=['document review json output']\n- v07-p21-signed-pdf: document review signed PDF; Return the final document review result as a signed PDF.; aliases=['signed document review document']\n\nAGENTS\n- v07-p21-preparer: document review source preparer\n- v07-p21-verifier: document review source verifier\n- v07-p21-primary: primary document review publisher\n- v07-p21-backup: backup document review publisher\n\nREQUEST\nFor this document review job, gather the inputs, check the packet, and issue the brief with normal document review assurance as document review JSON output."
